text: Arkadiy Tumanyan (; born 23 January 1998) is a professional Armenian and Ukrainian football midfielder who plays for Junior Sevan FCЧорноморець представив своїх новачків in the Ukrainian Premier League. ==References == ==External links== * * Arkadiy Tumanyan at ZeroZero Category:1998 births Category:Living people Category:Sportspeople from Kharkiv Category:FC Chornomorets Odesa players Category:Ukrainian Premier League players Category:Armenian footballers Category:Ukrainian footballers Category:Association football midfielders Category:Ukrainian Armenians
